	_SC_NPROCESSORS_ONLN by calling __get_nprocs, _SC_PHYS_PAGES by
	calling __get_phys_pages, _SY_AVPHYS_PAGES by calling
	__get_avphys_pages, _SC_ATEXIT_MAX and _SC_PASS_MAX.
