	_PC_SOCK_MAXBUF.
	* sysdeps/stub/fpathconf.c (fpathconf): Ditto.
	* sysdeps/posix/sysconf.c (sysconf): Add handling of new
	P1003.1g variables.
	* sysdeps/stub/sysconf.c (sysconf): Ditto.
